## üß† Key Concepts Demonstrated
- Natural Language Processing (NLP)
- Text preprocessing
- Stop-word removal
- Bag-of-Words representation
- Naive Bayes classification
- Model evaluation metrics

---

## üéØ Learning Outcomes
- Text must be converted to numeric features before modeling
- Feature cleaning strongly impacts performance
- Accuracy alone is insufficient ‚Äî precision & recall matter
- Confusion matrices provide deeper insight into model behavior

